Direct Known Subclasses:
ClarInfoAndFiles
public class RunInfoAndFiles
extends java.lang.Object

A single run, information and files

Contains run information (siteId, runId, problem info, language info, elapsed time (minutes), team info, whether the problem was solved, and other settings)

There may or may not be files in this class, use the getNumUserFiles() to determine whether there are files present.

See Also:
getNumUserFiles()
